22
00:01:19,494 --> 00:01:22,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sideswipe, a 5G heavyweight</i></b></font>

23
00:01:22,664 --> 00:01:24,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Runnin' right to the line, a hair's breadth</i>
<i>between offense and defense</i></b></font>

24
00:01:24,864 --> 00:01:25,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ba-ba-baaam!</i></b></font>

25
00:01:25,864 --> 00:01:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, I can step on the gas for</i>
<i>an easy victory, I still got it</i></b></font>

26
00:01:46,024 --> 00:01:47,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

27
00:01:47,284 --> 00:01:48,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have the day off today?</b></font>

28
00:01:48,654 --> 00:01:50,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--Takumi!</b></font>

29
00:01:50,824 --> 00:01:52,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I finally did it!</b></font>

30
00:01:52,464 --> 00:01:54,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did what?</b></font>

31
00:01:54,164 --> 00:01:55,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The turbo, man, the turbo!</b></font>

32
00:01:55,634 --> 00:02:00,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you before, right?! That I was
gonna add a turbo to the Levin!</b></font>

33
00:02:00,064 --> 00:02:01,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh...</b></font>

34
00:02:01,234 --> 00:02:03,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's at the shop right now.</b></font>

35
00:02:03,504 --> 00:02:06,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aah, I can't wait till the day I get it back!</b></font>

36
00:02:06,844 --> 00:02:08,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So Itsuki's Eight-Five will get an upgrade,</b></font>

37
00:02:08,844 --> 00:02:11,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>going from a slug to a plain old snail, huh?</b></font>

38
00:02:11,984 --> 00:02:15,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think you're saying, Iketani?</b></font>

39
00:02:15,214 --> 00:02:19,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll have you know they're expecting
it'll go to about 180 horsepower!</b></font>

40
00:02:19,354 --> 00:02:25,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In which case, it could even keep
up with your S13 on the uphill!</b></font>

41
00:02:25,264 --> 00:02:29,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll have that much output?
A turbo sure is incredible.</b></font>

42
00:02:29,694 --> 00:02:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, Takumi...</b></font>

43
00:02:32,334 --> 00:02:38,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard from Kenji. You even beat
those guys from the Toudou School.</b></font>

44
00:02:38,104 --> 00:02:40,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, somehow.</b></font>

45
00:02:40,044 --> 00:02:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it seems that Keisuke Takahashi
also won the uphill timed race!</b></font>

46
00:02:45,544 --> 00:02:47,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Toudou School couldn't do a thing, huh?</b></font>

47
00:02:47,784 --> 00:02:51,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D sure is incredible.</b></font>

48
00:02:51,384 --> 00:02:55,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if my Eight-Five turbo will
get me scouted for Project D, too.</b></font>

49
00:02:57,354 --> 00:02:59,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not gonna happen!</b></font>

50
00:03:05,534 --> 00:03:07,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomo!</b></font>

51
00:03:07,774 --> 00:03:11,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard you all lost.</b></font>

52
00:03:11,144 --> 00:03:14,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna hear the details.</b></font>

53
00:03:15,114 --> 00:03:19,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 5: The Starting Line to Victory"</b></font>

54
00:03:23,584 --> 00:03:28,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I think this incident will
be a good lesson for them.</b></font>

55
00:03:28,454 --> 00:03:31,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This kind of motivation is important, too.</b></font>

56
00:03:31,424 --> 00:03:36,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as you keep racing, you're gonna
run into different kinds of walls.</b></font>

57
00:03:36,164 --> 00:03:41,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For both Sakai and Daiki, this was
an encounter with one such wall.</b></font>

58
00:03:44,774 --> 00:03:48,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's only the guys who suffer through it
who can climb that wall and move onward.</b></font>

59
00:03:48,844 --> 00:03:51,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you hit a wall you can't climb,</b></font>

60
00:03:51,144 --> 00:03:54,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that's when you've reached
your limits as a driver.</b></font>

61
00:03:54,114 --> 00:03:56,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Tomoyuki...</b></font>

62
00:03:56,954 --> 00:04:03,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should still be able to climb any
number of the walls you're hitting now.</b></font>

63
00:04:03,194 --> 00:04:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is embarrassing.
You could tell, could you, Sir?</b></font>

64
00:04:06,694 --> 00:04:12,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I couldn't tell that much, I wouldn't
be fit to run the Toudou School.</b></font>

65
00:04:12,364 --> 00:04:15,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My "wall" is pretty intense.</b></font>

66
00:04:15,334 --> 00:04:20,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been made keenly aware that
in racing, having funds is everything.</b></font>

67
00:04:21,814 --> 00:04:25,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After losing on the straightaway,
I pushed myself too far,</b></font>

68
00:04:25,544 --> 00:04:29,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>making stupid mistakes
or getting into trouble.</b></font>

69
00:04:29,354 --> 00:04:31,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The team's morale is getting worse</b></font>

70
00:04:31,784 --> 00:04:37,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and with this economy, the sponsors
aren't lining up. The future looks grim.</b></font>

71
00:04:37,294 --> 00:04:41,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This may be one wall I'm
powerless against on my own.</b></font>

72
00:04:41,494 --> 00:04:44,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really don't know what I should do.</b></font>

73
00:04:44,904 --> 00:04:49,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's where you're wrong, Tomoyuki.
You've forgotten something very important.</b></font>

74
00:04:51,004 --> 00:04:54,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a problem I can guarantee lies with <i>you.</i></b></font>

75
00:04:54,344 --> 00:04:56,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Don't you get it?
--Sir...</b></font>

76
00:04:56,644 --> 00:05:01,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you give street racing a try?</b></font>

77
00:05:01,384 --> 00:05:03,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you being serious?</b></font>

78
00:05:03,484 --> 00:05:08,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who said not to do anything
stupid out on the street once turning pro!</b></font>

79
00:05:08,594 --> 00:05:11,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes you hafta be an idiot.</b></font>

80
00:05:11,924 --> 00:05:17,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just think of it like you'll be pullin' a fast
one on those street-racin' amateurs!</b></font>

81
00:05:17,334 --> 00:05:22,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll probably find the answer
you're lookin' for now...</b></font>

82
00:05:22,574 --> 00:05:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

83
00:05:25,044 --> 00:05:28,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Homemade Taste for Health and Beauty"</b></font>

84
00:05:25,044 --> 00:05:28,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Chilled Tofu with Dinner"</b></font>

85
00:05:34,184 --> 00:05:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How is it?</b></font>

86
00:05:36,014 --> 00:05:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's got pretty good balance.</b></font>

87
00:05:38,184 --> 00:05:40,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I did a light run there and back,</b></font>

88
00:05:40,224 --> 00:05:42,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and compared to when the
engine was first changed out,</b></font>

89
00:05:42,794 --> 00:05:45,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can charge downhill and it feels good.</b></font>

90
00:05:45,894 --> 00:05:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The suspension's a little tricky,
but it's come a long way.</b></font>

91
00:05:50,094 --> 00:05:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet this has made it easier to run races, too.</b></font>

92
00:05:52,864 --> 00:05:57,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it friggin' hasn't. The guys
we race keep getting better.</b></font>

93
00:05:57,034 --> 00:06:00,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like there's no way
I can keep on winning...</b></font>

94
00:06:04,414 --> 00:06:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course not. It's about time
you try losin' for a change.</b></font>

95
00:06:08,454 --> 00:06:10,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can learn a lot from losin'.</b></font>

96
00:06:10,754 --> 00:06:14,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Try losing"? How can you say it like that?</b></font>

97
00:06:14,454 --> 00:06:19,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're winning these as a <i>team,</i>
so I can't just go losing, now can I?</b></font>

98
00:06:19,724 --> 00:06:23,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Talk all you want, but no one
can perform above his means.</b></font>

99
00:06:23,964 --> 00:06:29,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A car's got a basic limit
it can't go faster than, too.</b></font>

100
00:06:29,334 --> 00:06:31,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, but still...</b></font>

101
00:06:31,004 --> 00:06:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd probably be a load off your mind
if you thought about it that way.</b></font>

102
00:06:35,774 --> 00:06:37,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, this car...</b></font>

103
00:06:37,274 --> 00:06:41,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I said we could share it, but it feels
like you've completely taken it from me.</b></font>

104
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:45,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not even fun for me to work on it anymore.</b></font>

105
00:06:45,324 --> 00:06:48,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe I'll buy one, a different one.</b></font>

106
00:06:48,594 --> 00:06:49,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A-Are you serious?</b></font>

107
00:06:49,754 --> 00:06:53,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll ask Masashi. If a bargain comes up,
I'll have him send it my way.</b></font>

108
00:06:53,824 --> 00:06:56,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you want to buy? What make?</b></font>

109
00:06:58,634 --> 00:07:00,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a secret.</b></font>

110
00:07:06,004 --> 00:07:08,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother, I'm coming in.</b></font>

111
00:07:08,114 --> 00:07:09,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

112
00:07:12,484 --> 00:07:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said we got a rematch
challenge from the Toudou School?</b></font>

113
00:07:16,054 --> 00:07:17,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From one of its graduates.</b></font>

114
00:07:17,614 --> 00:07:19,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A graduate?
--Yes.</b></font>

115
00:07:19,954 --> 00:07:21,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're accepting, right?</b></font>

116
00:07:25,364 --> 00:07:29,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Akechidaira</b></font>

117
00:07:25,364 --> 00:07:29,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Panorama Restaurant House"</b></font>

118
00:07:27,994 --> 00:07:30,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Is this Ryosuke?
--Yes.</b></font>

119
00:07:30,664 --> 00:07:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is Kyoichi Sudou.</b></font>

120
00:07:32,334 --> 00:07:35,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi? This is a surprise.</b></font>

121
00:07:35,234 --> 00:07:39,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got a rematch challenge from a
graduate of the Toudou School, right?</b></font>

122
00:07:39,404 --> 00:07:42,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd be better off not accepting it.</b></font>

123
00:07:42,744 --> 00:07:48,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you're not the type of guy to listen
when told not to do something, but listen up.</b></font>

124
00:07:48,084 --> 00:07:51,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your challenger this time is a pro racer!</b></font>

125
00:07:53,084 --> 00:07:54,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His name's Tomoyuki Tachi,</b></font>

126
00:07:54,894 --> 00:07:57,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and he's in a league all his own, even
compared to other Toudou School students.</b></font>

127
00:07:59,364 --> 00:08:04,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even the mighty Project D can't
be 100% assured of winning.</b></font>

128
00:08:04,334 --> 00:08:07,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If there's no way that this
can be avoided... Ryosuke.</b></font>

129
00:08:07,764 --> 00:08:09,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You do it!</b></font>

130
00:08:09,704 --> 00:08:14,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as the course is the street, and as
long as there's even a sliver of a chance,</b></font>

131
00:08:14,404 --> 00:08:17,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you need to race this yourself.</b></font>

132
00:08:41,574 --> 00:08:46,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible. The Toudou & Co. demo
cars are fast enough as it is,</b></font>

133
00:08:46,044 --> 00:08:49,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but having Tomo behind the steering wheel...</b></font>

134
00:08:49,374 --> 00:08:52,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got goose bumps just watching.</b></font>

135
00:08:52,484 --> 00:08:56,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just once, I'd like to be in
the passenger seat next to him.</b></font>

136
00:08:56,254 --> 00:09:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like he's in a whole other zone we
could race our entire lives and never reach.</b></font>

137
00:09:02,154 --> 00:09:07,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seeing this, I could care less whether
it's a revenge match against Project D,</b></font>

138
00:09:07,224 --> 00:09:10,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just definitely have to watch his next race!</b></font>

139
00:09:10,664 --> 00:09:14,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An all-out street race with
pro race driver Tomoyuki Tachi...</b></font>

140
00:09:14,464 --> 00:09:17,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There'll never be a second chance to see it!</b></font>

141
00:09:32,454 --> 00:09:34,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How is it?</b></font>

142
00:09:34,824 --> 00:09:39,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very nice. I have no complaints.</b></font>

143
00:09:39,124 --> 00:09:42,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any problems down the road will
be because of human emotion...</b></font>

144
00:09:42,364 --> 00:09:45,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Or rather, driver's preference.</b></font>

145
00:09:45,434 --> 00:09:48,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll make it fit <i>your</i> preference.
What do you want?</b></font>

146
00:09:48,774 --> 00:09:52,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? But...</b></font>

147
00:09:52,004 --> 00:09:54,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is it necessary to go that far</b></font>

148
00:09:54,444 --> 00:09:57,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when the car already has such
incredible racing capabilities?</b></font>

149
00:09:57,044 --> 00:09:59,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even though you said the
challengers are amateurs...</b></font>

150
00:09:59,814 --> 00:10:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may be just a street race,</b></font>

151
00:10:01,614 --> 00:10:04,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but if you don't give your all,
there's no point in doin' it.</b></font>

152
00:10:04,554 --> 00:10:05,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Listen, Tomoyuki...</b></font>

153
00:10:05,884 --> 00:10:07,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't think about needless details,</b></font>

154
00:10:07,624 --> 00:10:11,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and just treat this as if it were a real race.</b></font>

155
00:10:11,394 --> 00:10:15,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Show me the best job
you're capable of right now.</b></font>

156
00:10:19,034 --> 00:10:23,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. If you're going
to be that adamant about it,</b></font>

157
00:10:23,134 --> 00:10:27,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a small request to
make about the underbody.</b></font>

158
00:10:27,204 --> 00:10:32,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please retune it so that the rear comes
out a little more when entering corners.</b></font>

159
00:10:32,044 --> 00:10:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The way I drive now,
that will trim my race time.</b></font>

160
00:10:36,514 --> 00:10:40,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, understood. No problem.</b></font>

161
00:10:48,234 --> 00:10:51,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure does give off a different
impression, doesn't it?</b></font>

162
00:10:51,334 --> 00:10:53,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just with one new hood...</b></font>

163
00:10:54,104 --> 00:10:59,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Based on Ryosuke's advice, I've tried
to make the Eight-Six more lightweight.</b></font>

164
00:10:59,244 --> 00:11:03,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Going forward, we plan to try
several such small modifications.</b></font>

165
00:11:03,444 --> 00:11:06,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone, gather round.
The meeting will now begin.</b></font>

166
00:11:08,914 --> 00:11:13,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is footage of the race
course shot just today.</b></font>

167
00:11:13,224 --> 00:11:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you watch this, I think you'll understand.</b></font>

168
00:11:15,354 --> 00:11:20,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This particular stage is a mix,
half uphill and half downhill.</b></font>

169
00:11:20,464 --> 00:11:25,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that case, who runs it, me or Fujiwara?</b></font>

170
00:11:25,104 --> 00:11:28,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We will decide that once we reach the course.</b></font>

171
00:11:28,034 --> 00:11:33,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both cars will do a practice run, and I will
review the results to make my decision.</b></font>

172
00:11:33,274 --> 00:11:39,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the hell? It's gonna be me,</i>
<i>of course! I'm the ace driver!</i></b></font>

173
00:11:39,544 --> 00:11:47,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is important, so I'll say it up front:
our opponent is from the Toudou School.</b></font>

174
00:11:47,784 --> 00:11:51,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's more, he's an established pro racer.</b></font>

175
00:11:53,494 --> 00:11:55,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A pro?! No way!</b></font>

176
00:11:55,564 --> 00:11:58,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how you look at it,
this is a bad idea, Ryosuke.</b></font>

177
00:11:58,904 --> 00:12:02,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our guys will run right into his traps!</b></font>

178
00:12:02,304 --> 00:12:05,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right! This is playing dirty!</b></font>

179
00:12:05,244 --> 00:12:08,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There will be no way of knowing
unless we challenge him.</b></font>

180
00:12:08,004 --> 00:12:11,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've thought it over,
and decided that we shall do it.</b></font>

181
00:12:11,984 --> 00:12:15,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We shall never run away from any opponent.</b></font>

182
00:12:15,684 --> 00:12:18,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is the motto of Project D!</b></font>

183
00:12:18,754 --> 00:12:21,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me do it, brother.</b></font>

184
00:12:21,824 --> 00:12:24,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the stage is a mix of uphill and downhill,</b></font>

185
00:12:24,424 --> 00:12:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>then with its level of power, the FD should
have the advantage over the Eight-Six.</b></font>

186
00:12:28,834 --> 00:12:29,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right!</b></font>

187
00:12:29,834 --> 00:12:33,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke. Do not make me
say the same thing twice.</b></font>

188
00:12:34,534 --> 00:12:39,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I said, I will decide who races
once we arrive at the course!</b></font>

189
00:12:52,854 --> 00:12:54,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomo.</b></font>

190
00:12:54,284 --> 00:12:55,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah. Daiki.</b></font>

191
00:12:55,994 --> 00:13:00,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D will start their practice runs tonight.</b></font>

192
00:13:00,024 --> 00:13:04,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What will you do? Would you
like to go take a look later?</b></font>

193
00:13:04,664 --> 00:13:06,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll be racing till close to dawn,</b></font>

194
00:13:06,404 --> 00:13:08,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>tuning their cars while running the course--</b></font>

195
00:13:08,234 --> 00:13:11,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like they're playing racecar.</b></font>

196
00:13:11,674 --> 00:13:17,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're doing the same thing we
normally do when racing a circuit, eh?</b></font>

197
00:13:17,244 --> 00:13:23,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I don't really
know what Mr. Toudou is thinking.</b></font>

198
00:13:23,814 --> 00:13:26,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think he knows I'm stressed</b></font>

199
00:13:26,224 --> 00:13:30,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is probably trying to give
me a chance to snap out of it.</b></font>

200
00:13:30,654 --> 00:13:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The thing is, there's no reason for me
to look forward to some street race.</b></font>

201
00:13:36,834 --> 00:13:42,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm only doing this because I
think it's best to do what he says.</b></font>

202
00:13:42,504 --> 00:13:47,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And since I've decided to do it, I won't pull
any punches, even against an amateur.</b></font>

203
00:13:47,574 --> 00:13:51,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You all just watch closely and see
how big a difference there is</b></font>

204
00:13:51,214 --> 00:13:53,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>between pros and amateurs!</b></font>

205
00:14:04,524 --> 00:14:08,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a tough course that
incorporates all different types.</b></font>

206
00:14:08,694 --> 00:14:12,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cars' condition, drivers' techniques...</b></font>

207
00:14:12,134 --> 00:14:15,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This course will require the best of both.</b></font>

208
00:14:15,774 --> 00:14:19,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As always, run five races at 80%.</b></font>

209
00:14:19,644 --> 00:14:21,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is not the Toudou School's course,</b></font>

210
00:14:21,914 --> 00:14:25,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but they should already
have raced it before us.</b></font>

211
00:14:25,384 --> 00:14:27,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Concentrate, and head out!</b></font>

212
00:14:41,594 --> 00:14:44,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke certainly is taking this seriously.</b></font>

213
00:14:44,234 --> 00:14:45,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, he is.</b></font>

214
00:14:45,734 --> 00:14:48,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I say we take our time with it.</b></font>

215
00:14:48,404 --> 00:14:50,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know whether we'll race or not,</b></font>

216
00:14:50,604 --> 00:14:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but we should at least
get everything done right.</b></font>

217
00:14:53,074 --> 00:14:55,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Okay.
--As always...</b></font>

218
00:14:55,414 --> 00:14:59,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...our real enemy is the course.</b></font>

219
00:14:59,314 --> 00:15:00,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here I go.</b></font>

220
00:15:04,314 --> 00:15:06,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke...</b></font>

221
00:15:06,254 --> 00:15:10,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't like you, heading out
alone to scout out the course.</b></font>

222
00:15:10,924 --> 00:15:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's more, taking the FC with you...</b></font>

223
00:15:13,694 --> 00:15:18,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is no special meaning in
my having brought my own car.</b></font>

224
00:15:18,094 --> 00:15:23,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The important thing was simply to grab
the steering wheel and know the course.</b></font>

225
00:15:23,134 --> 00:15:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--However, it...
--What is it?</b></font>

226
00:15:25,704 --> 00:15:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the contrary, it has
made me more confused.</b></font>

227
00:15:30,014 --> 00:15:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fumihiro, you give the orders in my stead.</b></font>

228
00:15:33,884 --> 00:15:36,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The same routine as always,
so there should be no problems.</b></font>

229
00:15:36,554 --> 00:15:39,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! And what are you going to do?</b></font>

230
00:15:39,324 --> 00:15:41,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sleep.</b></font>

231
00:15:41,054 --> 00:15:42,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-Hey!</b></font>

232
00:15:42,824 --> 00:15:45,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been absorbed with
a clinical pathology report</b></font>

233
00:15:45,564 --> 00:15:48,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and have just remembered I've worked
until the early hours for three days now.</b></font>

234
00:15:48,894 --> 00:15:52,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought my head was
operating rather sluggishly.</b></font>

235
00:15:52,234 --> 00:15:53,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do not wake me.</b></font>

236
00:16:14,084 --> 00:16:15,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I get it.</i></b></font>

237
00:16:15,754 --> 00:16:17,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Not only are there steep ups and downs,</i></b></font>

238
00:16:17,224 --> 00:16:22,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>there are so many variables to this</i>
<i>course that it's hard to keep balanced.</i></b></font>

239
00:16:23,664 --> 00:16:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess that's what my brother meant</i>
<i>when he said this was a tough course.</i></b></font>

240
00:16:36,714 --> 00:16:41,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder how my skills will</i>
<i>stack up against a pro racer.</i></b></font>

241
00:16:41,214 --> 00:16:43,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is my best chance to test it out!</i></b></font>

242
00:16:46,284 --> 00:16:49,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How on earth is this going to turn out?</b></font>

243
00:16:49,124 --> 00:16:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really worried about this...</b></font>

244
00:16:50,954 --> 00:16:54,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There it is again.
That old Fumihiro anxiousness.</b></font>

245
00:16:54,624 --> 00:16:59,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not it. This time,
something is really strange.</b></font>

246
00:16:59,304 --> 00:17:01,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I've known him for a long time.</b></font>

247
00:17:01,804 --> 00:17:04,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

248
00:17:04,474 --> 00:17:07,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He would never use the Eight-Six
on this course, would he?</b></font>

249
00:17:07,574 --> 00:17:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. That's what I'm thinking.</b></font>

250
00:17:14,544 --> 00:17:17,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What are you planning, Ryosuke?</i></b></font>

251
00:17:17,414 --> 00:17:20,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No... It couldn't be!</i></b></font>

252
00:17:42,314 --> 00:17:45,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's finished.</b></font>

253
00:17:45,184 --> 00:17:48,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All done, Keisuke.</b></font>

254
00:17:48,144 --> 00:17:49,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

255
00:18:06,864 --> 00:18:10,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Italian Fair"</b></font>

256
00:18:08,474 --> 00:18:11,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My back hurts!</b></font>

257
00:18:11,004 --> 00:18:14,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't get a good night's
sleep in a car, can you?</b></font>

258
00:18:14,874 --> 00:18:17,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke's pretty incredible
about that, isn't he?</b></font>

259
00:18:17,714 --> 00:18:21,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He can sleep soundly and not wake up at all!</b></font>

260
00:18:21,144 --> 00:18:23,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our great leader...</b></font>

261
00:18:23,014 --> 00:18:25,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's nothing to make fun of, Matsumoto!</b></font>

262
00:18:25,624 --> 00:18:34,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I swear! Only just yesterday, he let
us know just how important he is.</b></font>

263
00:18:34,224 --> 00:18:40,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An organization can't perform
smoothly if its "brain" isn't functioning.</b></font>

264
00:18:40,504 --> 00:18:44,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our spirits are low and
we're operating disjointedly.</b></font>

265
00:18:44,074 --> 00:18:48,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And he should know it.</b></font>

266
00:18:48,644 --> 00:18:52,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how you look at it,
this time around, it's strange.</b></font>

267
00:18:52,344 --> 00:18:54,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

268
00:18:54,084 --> 00:18:57,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is just between you and me, Matsumoto.</b></font>

269
00:18:57,314 --> 00:19:02,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think Ryosuke can't come up with
a simulation that will let us win.</b></font>

270
00:19:02,594 --> 00:19:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After exploring any and all possibilities,
if he still can't find a way we can win...</b></font>

271
00:19:18,234 --> 00:19:20,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's Ryosuke for you.</b></font>

272
00:19:20,944 --> 00:19:24,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Configuring the cars should
have taken till morning,</b></font>

273
00:19:24,274 --> 00:19:27,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but Ryosuke was somehow able
to do it last night in two hours.</b></font>

274
00:19:27,944 --> 00:19:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wondered what was going on
for a while there, but...</b></font>

275
00:19:30,754 --> 00:19:33,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke sure is incredible!</b></font>

276
00:19:37,224 --> 00:19:39,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're here! The Toudou School!</b></font>

277
00:19:49,034 --> 00:19:50,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bring me a flashlight!</b></font>

278
00:19:50,604 --> 00:19:52,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And a jack!</b></font>

279
00:19:53,644 --> 00:19:57,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looks like the boss man
finally showed his face.</b></font>

280
00:19:57,244 --> 00:20:00,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I immediately knew which
one was today's driver!</b></font>

281
00:20:00,084 --> 00:20:01,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, too.</b></font>

282
00:20:01,814 --> 00:20:04,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's different, isn't he?</b></font>

283
00:20:07,654 --> 00:20:11,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, Fujiwara. Come here a moment.</b></font>

284
00:20:13,224 --> 00:20:17,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After reviewing yesterday's data,
I've made my decision.</b></font>

285
00:20:21,564 --> 00:20:24,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Today, the Eight-Six will ride.</b></font>

286
00:20:24,004 --> 00:20:26,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You, Fujiwara.</b></font>

287
00:20:28,674 --> 00:20:30,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on a minute, brother!</b></font>

288
00:20:30,574 --> 00:20:34,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had a better time in the practice runs!</b></font>

289
00:20:34,284 --> 00:20:36,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that.</b></font>

290
00:20:36,154 --> 00:20:40,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then unless you explain, I can't
accept it. Why the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

291
00:20:40,654 --> 00:20:45,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will explain later. There's
something I must do now, quickly.</b></font>

292
00:20:45,264 --> 00:20:46,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara.</b></font>

293
00:20:46,694 --> 00:20:51,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get in my car's passenger seat.
I shall lecture you as we ride.</b></font>

294
00:21:03,714 --> 00:21:07,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Brother... this isn't right!</i></b></font>

295
00:21:07,714 --> 00:21:10,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, don't let it get to you.</b></font>

296
00:21:10,614 --> 00:21:14,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What Ryosuke does,
he does for an important reason.</b></font>

297
00:21:14,024 --> 00:21:17,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I know that!
--Keisuke!</b></font>

298
00:21:17,194 --> 00:21:21,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And knowing that just
makes it more disgraceful!</b></font>

299
00:21:47,424 --> 00:21:49,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A-Awesome!</b></font>

300
00:21:52,594 --> 00:21:55,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just once, I'd like to wear something like that!</b></font>

301
00:21:55,694 --> 00:21:59,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Idiot. These are like battle fatigues.</b></font>

302
00:21:59,504 --> 00:22:03,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you put these on, playtime is over.</b></font>

303
00:22:03,034 --> 00:22:06,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You <i>fight</i>, with the pride of a professional.</b></font>

304
00:22:06,104 --> 00:22:07,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomo.</b></font>

305
00:22:07,374 --> 00:22:09,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even one of our demo cars</b></font>

306
00:22:09,414 --> 00:22:13,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will lose to an FD on a straightaway.
Don't let your guard down.</b></font>

307
00:22:13,844 --> 00:22:19,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I already have a counter-strategy in mind.
That's why I had the car tuned to my specs.</b></font>

308
00:22:19,224 --> 00:22:22,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just leave the rest to me.</b></font>

309
00:22:36,534 --> 00:22:39,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are the Eight-Six's preparations complete?</b></font>

310
00:22:39,144 --> 00:22:43,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's already done warming up.
It's good to go anytime.</b></font>

311
00:22:43,244 --> 00:22:45,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very well, let's start. Fumihiro.</b></font>

312
00:22:45,914 --> 00:22:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it.</b></font>

313
00:22:53,954 --> 00:22:55,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, let's begin.</b></font>

314
00:22:55,654 --> 00:22:58,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's plenty of road width,
so we'd like to start</b></font>

315
00:22:58,894 --> 00:23:01,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with a simultaneous, side-by-side dash.</b></font>

316
00:23:01,424 --> 00:23:04,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine. I leave it all up to you.</b></font>

317
00:23:04,164 --> 00:23:08,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. Okay, line up your cars!</b></font>

318
00:23:17,014 --> 00:23:20,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what the hell? For real, the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

319
00:23:30,994 --> 00:23:33,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Didn't see this one coming, eh?</b></font>

320
00:23:33,624 --> 00:23:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the meaning of this?</b></font>

321
00:23:36,834 --> 00:23:40,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They don't disappoint,
those guys from Gunma.</b></font>

322
00:23:43,474 --> 00:23:47,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We were 100% sure they'd come with the FD,</b></font>

323
00:23:47,874 --> 00:23:50,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>meaning they've avoided all our preparations.</b></font>

324
00:23:50,944 --> 00:23:54,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To think they'd use some
underpowered Eight-Six...</b></font>

325
00:24:26,014 --> 00:24:29,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is quite the insult to us, and to Tomoyuki.</b></font>

326
00:24:29,814 --> 00:24:35,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, that makes it all the more interesting.</b></font>

327
00:24:35,154 --> 00:24:39,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right! Starting the countdown!</b></font>

328
00:24:49,674 --> 00:24:53,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five! Four! Three!</b></font>

329
00:24:53,104 --> 00:24:55,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two! One!</b></font>

330
00:24:55,104 --> 00:24:56,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

331
00:25:02,384 --> 00:25:05,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right! His front section's
pulled halfway ahead!</b></font>

332
00:25:07,124 --> 00:25:09,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which will it be?</b></font>

333
00:25:09,554 --> 00:25:12,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which one will enter the corner first?!</b></font>

334
00:25:46,764 --> 00:25:48,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hey, the coming of a new generation</i></b></font>

335
00:25:48,764 --> 00:25:51,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Calling now for the arrival of a new era</i></b></font>

336
00:25:51,664 --> 00:25:56,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How long are you going to</i>
<i>pretend you've forgotten?</i></b></font>

337
00:25:56,804 --> 00:26:01,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Tension that seems like it'll</i>
<i>rip my heart) This heartache...</i></b></font>

338
00:26:01,904 --> 00:26:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Within those eyes,</i>
<i>something that can't be held back...</i></b></font>

339
00:26:06,914 --> 00:26:12,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Yeah, this image that won't let me go)</i>
<i>...stares intently at the night</i></b></font>

340
00:26:12,354 --> 00:26:22,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yes, the two who didn't even know how</i></b></font>

341
00:26:22,194 --> 00:26:27,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>to reach out and touch someone's</i>
<i>heart are already, from here...</i></b></font>

342
00:26:27,134 --> 00:26:32,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Hey, the coming of a new generation,</i>
<i>Check it, This will blast your love)</i></b></font>

343
00:26:32,274 --> 00:26:36,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, break off the barrier</i></b></font>

344
00:26:36,614 --> 00:26:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Strike the sleeping dream awake</i>
<i>(Skillz enough to rend the night!)</i></b></font>

345
00:26:42,314 --> 00:26:46,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, stronger than fire</i></b></font>

346
00:26:46,784 --> 00:26:53,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A risky tune that rocks the times</i></b></font>

347
00:26:53,694 --> 00:26:57,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire</i></b></font>

348
00:26:57,034 --> 00:27:01,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Calling now for the arrival of a new era,</i>
<i>be what you wanna be)</i></b></font>

349
00:27:01,304 --> 00:27:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire</i></b></font>

350
00:27:03,834 --> 00:27:07,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, whoa whoa whoa yeah</i></b></font>

351
00:27:07,144 --> 00:27:12,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Calling now for the arrival of a new era,</i>
<i>break what you wanna break)</i></b></font>

